---
title: One-Pan Turkey Dinner  with Mushrooms and Green Beans
description: This quick and comforting one-pan meal brings together tender turkey, hearty beans and earthy mushrooms in a rich and creamy thyme-infused sauce. Simmered with fluffy rice, it's a perfect balance of cozy and convenient, making it an easy weeknight favourite.

